-- China Drafts Alternative Energy Development Plan, Securities News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-05T00:10:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/china-drafts-alternative-energy-development-plan-securities-news-reports.html

          
          
             China has drafted a development plan
for alternative energy that includes a model alternative energy
base in the northwest Xinjiang region, the Shanghai Securities
News reported, citing Zhang Guobao, vice chairman of the
National Development and Reform Commission.  
